                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1'>INSIGHTS:</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1'>• Car is the most efficient travel mode overall.</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1'>• Air travel has the highest average wait time.</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1'>• Train travel shows the highest average travel cost.</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1'>• Bus and train modes cover the longest travel distances.</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1'>• Most travel wait times are concentrated below 70 minutes.</run>
                  </formatted-text>
